																		2013 Guide Overhaul
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aelanna" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(334454); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=334454&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610202523" alt="Aelanna" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=334454)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aelanna" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(334454); return false;" >Aelanna</a></span> <span class="odate time_1389420377 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">11 Jan 2014 06:06</span>
														</div>
